    - side: 1
      characterController: {fileID: 9100000, guid: 79ca830ccddbb73458eb59262616464d, type: 2}
      boxColor: {fileID: -5631079478217351519, guid: 4be1d46c47a742d4d90863ffcfef67c0, type: 3}
      avatarAnimationName: Burumi_Happy
      text: 'Anywayss, Im you guide to learn the playstyle of this game okiees pookies? '
    - side: 1
      characterController: {fileID: 9100000, guid: 79ca830ccddbb73458eb59262616464d, type: 2}
      boxColor: {fileID: -5631079478217351519, guid: 4be1d46c47a742d4d90863ffcfef67c0, type: 3}
      avatarAnimationName: Burumi_Happy
      text: Let us begin~
  - sequenceName: IntroProgression
    lines:
    - side: 1
      characterController: {fileID: 9100000, guid: 79ca830ccddbb73458eb59262616464d, type: 2}
      boxColor: {fileID: -5631079478217351519, guid: 4be1d46c47a742d4d90863ffcfef67c0, type: 3}
      avatarAnimationName: Burumi_Idle
      text: The game condition is very simple.
    - side: 1
      characterController: {fileID: 9100000, guid: 79ca830ccddbb73458eb59262616464d, type: 2}
      boxColor: {fileID: -5631079478217351519, guid: 4be1d46c47a742d4d90863ffcfef67c0, type: 3}
      avatarAnimationName: Burumi_Said
      text: 'Catch the Thief before the destination above the progression bar comes
        to an end... Got It? '
  - sequenceName: PoisonTutorial
    lines:
    - side: 1
      characterController: {fileID: 9100000, guid: 79ca830ccddbb73458eb59262616464d, type: 2}
      boxColor: {fileID: 0}
      avatarAnimationName: Burumi_Complain
      text: Watch out, a poison barrel! You can't type that.
    - side: 1
      characterController: {fileID: 9100000, guid: 79ca830ccddbb73458eb59262616464d, type: 2}
      boxColor: {fileID: 0}
      avatarAnimationName: Burumi_Said
      text: Press Spacebar to jump over it, or you'll get dizzy
  - sequenceName: PunchTutorial
    lines:
    - side: 1
      characterController: {fileID: 9100000, guid: 79ca830ccddbb73458eb59262616464d, type: 2}
      boxColor: {fileID: -5631079478217351519, guid: 4be1d46c47a742d4d90863ffcfef67c0, type: 3}
      avatarAnimationName: Burumi_Complain
      text: Another trap! Jump over it with Spacebar!
    - side: 1
      characterController: {fileID: 9100000, guid: 79ca830ccddbb73458eb59262616464d, type: 2}
      boxColor: {fileID: -5631079478217351519, guid: 4be1d46c47a742d4d90863ffcfef67c0, type: 3}
      avatarAnimationName: Burumi_Task
      text: If you hit it, you'll get stunned and lose health!
  - sequenceName: FoodTutorial
    lines:
    - side: 1
      characterController: {fileID: 9100000, guid: 79ca830ccddbb73458eb59262616464d, type: 2}
      boxColor: {fileID: -5631079478217351519, guid: 4be1d46c47a742d4d90863ffcfef67c0, type: 3}
      avatarAnimationName: Burumi_Task
      text: Look, food! Quickly, type the word attached to it before it hits you!
  - sequenceName: AmmoTutorial
    lines:
    - side: 1
      characterController: {fileID: 9100000, guid: 79ca830ccddbb73458eb59262616464d, type: 2}
      boxColor: {fileID: -5631079478217351519, guid: 4be1d46c47a742d4d90863ffcfef67c0, type: 3}
      avatarAnimationName: Burumi_Joy
      text: 'Nice typing! The food went into your bag. '
    - side: 1
      characterController: {fileID: 9100000, guid: 79ca830ccddbb73458eb59262616464d, type: 2}
      boxColor: {fileID: -5631079478217351519, guid: 4be1d46c47a742d4d90863ffcfef67c0, type: 3}
      avatarAnimationName: Burumi_Said
      text: 'Press Enter to throw it back at the Thief and slow him down! '
    - side: 1
      characterController: {fileID: 9100000, guid: 79ca830ccddbb73458eb59262616464d, type: 2}
      boxColor: {fileID: -5631079478217351519, guid: 4be1d46c47a742d4d90863ffcfef67c0, type: 3}
      avatarAnimationName: Burumi_Idle
      text: You can store up to 5 only otherwise...
  - sequenceName: ThiefKnockedTutorial
    lines:
    - side: 1
      characterController: {fileID: 9100000, guid: 79ca830ccddbb73458eb59262616464d, type: 2}
      boxColor: {fileID: -5631079478217351519, guid: 4be1d46c47a742d4d90863ffcfef67c0, type: 3}
      avatarAnimationName: Burumi_Task
      text: Bullseye! You knocked him out of the sky!
    - side: 0
      characterController: {fileID: 9100000, guid: 84cb4167ffe048747a67572b3a040c08, type: 2}
      boxColor: {fileID: 518374836525813700, guid: 9cd9f743f8d609b4fab38ef8801784bc, type: 3}
      avatarAnimationName: Erufinn_Huh
      text: I did good job?
    - side: 1
      characterController: {fileID: 9100000, guid: 79ca830ccddbb73458eb59262616464d, type: 2}
      boxColor: {fileID: -5631079478217351519, guid: 4be1d46c47a742d4d90863ffcfef67c0, type: 3}
      avatarAnimationName: Burumi_Joy
      text: Yep! He just tumbled and your closer to catch him!
  - sequenceName: TutorialWin
    lines:
    - side: 1
      characterController: {fileID: 9100000, guid: 79ca830ccddbb73458eb59262616464d, type: 2}
      boxColor: {fileID: -5631079478217351519, guid: 4be1d46c47a742d4d90863ffcfef67c0, type: 3}
      avatarAnimationName: Burumi_Task
      text: Congratulations! You got the gist of this simple game!
    - side: 0
      characterController: {fileID: 9100000, guid: 84cb4167ffe048747a67572b3a040c08, type: 2}
      boxColor: {fileID: 518374836525813700, guid: 9cd9f743f8d609b4fab38ef8801784bc, type: 3}
      avatarAnimationName: Erufinn_Huh
      text: Woah fr fr? Walahi?
    - side: 1
      characterController: {fileID: 9100000, guid: 79ca830ccddbb73458eb59262616464d, type: 2}
      boxColor: {fileID: -5631079478217351519, guid: 4be1d46c47a742d4d90863ffcfef67c0, type: 3}
      avatarAnimationName: Burumi_Idle
      text: ...
    - side: 1
      characterController: {fileID: 9100000, guid: 79ca830ccddbb73458eb59262616464d, type: 2}
      boxColor: {fileID: -5631079478217351519, guid: 4be1d46c47a742d4d90863ffcfef67c0, type: 3}
      avatarAnimationName: Burumi_Happy
      text: Anyways you caught the thief and learned the game mechanic but it gets
        more unique from this. Are you ready?
  - sequenceName: TutorialLose
    lines:
    - side: 1
      characterController: {fileID: 9100000, guid: 79ca830ccddbb73458eb59262616464d, type: 2}
      boxColor: {fileID: -5631079478217351519, guid: 4be1d46c47a742d4d90863ffcfef67c0, type: 3}
      avatarAnimationName: Burumi_Complain
      text: Skill Issue.
    - side: 1
      characterController: {fileID: 9100000, guid: 79ca830ccddbb73458eb59262616464d, type: 2}
      boxColor: {fileID: -5631079478217351519, guid: 4be1d46c47a742d4d90863ffcfef67c0, type: 3}
      avatarAnimationName: Burumi_Said
      text: You lost! The Thief got away before you could catch up to him. Try playing
        smartly this time.
    - side: 1
      characterController: {fileID: 9100000, guid: 79ca830ccddbb73458eb59262616464d, type: 2}
      boxColor: {fileID: -5631079478217351519, guid: 4be1d46c47a742d4d90863ffcfef67c0, type: 3}
      avatarAnimationName: Burumi_Task
      text: Are you ready to try again?
  dialogueOverlay: {fileID: 1123834944}
